"      Rudwaleit M, van der Heijde D, Landew&eacute; R, et al. The development of Assessment of SpondyloArthritis international Society classification criteria for axial spondyloarthritis (part II): validation and final selection. Ann Rheum Dis 2009; 68:777.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
