"      Rudwaleit M, van der Heijde D, Landew&eacute; R, et al. The Assessment of SpondyloArthritis International Society classification criteria for peripheral spondyloarthritis and for spondyloarthritis in general. Ann Rheum Dis 2011; 70:25.",
"     </a>",
